      %h6 Database security for developers
  .row.features.spacy
    .large-4.column
      %h4
        %i.icon-lock
        &nbsp;
        End-to-end encryption
      %p Stay in control of your data. Cryodex applies strong encryption to your data before it is sent to the cloud. Private encryption keys never leave your servers.
    .large-4.column
      %h4
        %i.icon-tasks
        &nbsp;
        Transparent security
      %p Security that breaks applications is pointless. Cryodex preserves the ability to sort, search and retrieve encrypted data without requiring modifications to application code.
    .large-4.column
      %h4
        %i.icon-cloud
        &nbsp;
        Easy integration
      %p Integrate Cryodex in your existing application in less than 5 lines of code. Our encryption proxy works behind the scenes to protect your data.
      
  .row
    .large-12.column.text-center
      %a#request-info.button{href: "/contact"} Request more information
